snippet.title: Cursed Angel: Time Paradox - PC Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer for a upcoming RPG/RTS PC game: Cursed Angel - Time Paradox.
You can get more information about the game at https://store.steampowered.com/app/2176090/Cursed_Angel_Time_Paradox/?beta=0

Love or revenge? Save the world or save your lover? You must choose careful in this RPG Strategy game, or you can be trapped in a time loop and never get out.
